name: INGetCarLockStatusIntentResponseCode
desc: Constants indicating the status of the response.

items.name: case failure
items.desc: An error code indicating that you were unable to get the car’s lock status.

items.name: case failureRequiringAppLaunch
items.desc: An error code indicating that the user must launch your app to get the car’s lock status.

items.name: case inProgress
items.desc: A response code indicating that you are getting the car’s lock status but do not yet have the results.

items.name: case ready
items.desc: A response code indicating that you are ready to handle the intent.

items.name: case success
items.desc: A response code indicating that you have successfully handled the intent.

items.name: case unspecified
items.desc: A response code indicating that the status was not specified.
